I was hoping we could
talk about everything

4
00:00:26,659 --> 00:00:28,528
we haven't really gotten to say yet.

5
00:00:29,095 --> 00:00:30,497
That's what I wanted to say.

6
00:00:31,131 --> 00:00:33,933
Yeah. There's still a lot
we don't know about each other.

7
00:00:38,705 --> 00:00:41,741
It's not much, but we still have six days.

8
00:00:41,808 --> 00:00:42,809
That's right.

9
00:00:42,876 --> 00:00:46,012
We'll have time to talk,
just the two of us.

10
00:00:49,949 --> 00:00:50,850
Mmm.

11
