<i>They're sprouting!</i>

12
00:00:58,458 --> 00:01:01,161
- <i>They're really blooming.</i>
- <i>Spring has come.</i>

13
00:01:04,898 --> 00:01:06,332
- Ta-da.
- Wow.

14
00:01:07,033 --> 00:01:09,602
- What've you got?
- What's this? What's in the box?

15
00:01:09,669 --> 00:01:12,405
- We had these made for everyone.
- <i>Wait, don't tell me…</i>

16
00:01:12,472 --> 00:01:14,340
These are hoodies and T-shirts!

17
00:01:14,407 --> 00:01:15,942
<i>Wow, that's exciting!</i>

18
00:01:16,576 --> 00:01:18,578
- Oh my gosh, this is great.
- So excited!

19
00:01:18,645 --> 00:01:20,880
- Nice gray color.
- Oh, the gray came out really nice!

20
00:01:20,947 --> 00:01:22,382
- Look!
- Open one up.

21
00:01:22,449 --> 00:01:23,516
- I'll look.
- Okay!

22
00:01:23,583 --> 00:01:25,018
- Oh wow!
- So cute!

23
00:01:25,085 --> 00:01:26,386
- Nice!
- So cute.

24
00:01:26,453 --> 00:01:28,321
- These are great.
- Not bad, huh?

25
00:01:28,388 --> 00:01:29,289
Really good.

26
00:01:29,355 --> 00:01:31,491
- How cute!
- So cute!

27
00:01:31,558 --> 00:01:34,994
I drew ten flowers,
including ones for the members

28
00:01:35,061 --> 00:01:36,763
who already left the Green Room.

29
00:01:36,830 --> 00:01:40,800
Green is for Taeheon,
and pink is, of course, for Jobu.

30
00:01:40,867 --> 00:01:43,503
- William gets brown.
- Yeah, William is brown.

31
00:01:43,570 --> 00:01:46,639
- What about the front?
- And in the front…

32
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:52,612
It symbolizes the ten of us arriving
here with our own little buds,

33
00:01:52,679 --> 00:01:57,016
blooming into flowers in this place,
and then stepping out from here.

34
00:01:57,083 --> 00:01:58,251
Ah, I see.

35
00:01:58,318 --> 00:01:59,953
So are we choosing which to wear?

36
00:02:00,019 --> 00:02:02,388
- I want the hoodie.
- I'll go with the hoodie.

37
00:02:02,455 --> 00:02:04,390
I'm happy we can match.

38
00:02:05,191 --> 00:02:06,693
Oh!

39
00:02:06,759 --> 00:02:08,761
Oh.

40
00:02:10,964 --> 00:02:14,567
"There are five days left in our shared
life together in the Green Room."

41
00:02:17,704 --> 00:02:21,508
"Starting tomorrow, we embark
on our two-night trip to Sapporo!"

42
00:02:21,574 --> 00:02:23,910
<i>That's wild.</i>

43
00:02:23,977 --> 00:02:28,748
"And today marks
the final day of the coffee truck."

44
00:02:28,815 --> 00:02:30,416
- Hmm.
- Hmm.

45
00:02:30,483 --> 00:02:34,087
"Please discuss and decide the shift
among yourselves."

46
00:02:34,654 --> 00:02:35,688
Oh.

47
00:02:36,322 --> 00:02:37,991
- I wanna go with everyone.
- Really?

48
00:02:38,057 --> 00:02:40,260
- I wanna work at the coffee truck.
- Let's all go.

49
00:02:40,326 --> 00:02:42,962
- Yeah, let's all go.
- Wanna go wear the hoodies there?

50
