Let's wear them.

51
00:02:44,297 --> 00:02:45,665
Who's flipping the name tags?

52
00:02:45,732 --> 00:02:48,168
- Why don't we each flip our own?
- Good idea.

53
00:02:56,809 --> 00:02:59,078
- It's really the last time.
- <i>It's really ending.</i>

54
00:02:59,145 --> 00:03:00,547
<i>It's sad, huh?</i>

55
00:03:04,484 --> 00:03:05,785
Ugh, I'm sad.

56
00:03:12,692 --> 00:03:14,627
Let's do this!

57
00:03:16,362 --> 00:03:18,398
THE LAST DAY!
US, JOURNEY, COFFEE

58
00:03:18,464 --> 00:03:20,833
WE ARE SEVEN PEOPLE LIVING TOGETHER
AND SELLING COFFEE

59
00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:23,403
<i>One day, I'll talk to you</i>

60
