- Two chocolate milks, please.
- Two, got it.

72
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,962
Got it, thank you so much.

73
00:03:49,028 --> 00:03:50,697
What size would you like?

74
00:03:50,763 --> 00:03:53,499
<i>My mind, my mind</i>

75
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:58,905
<i>Whatever, miles away</i>
<i>Girl, I want you to know</i>

76
